additional_info: We are proud to introduce the very first session of “Rank Up with Syeta”, our brand-new talk series. The first session is conducted by Mr. Pasindu Upendra, Founder of Toad Creatives, on “Freelancing on Upwork”. This session focuses on giving you clear insight and understanding about the Upwork platform, and how to kickstart freelancing on it. All enthusiasts, either new or experienced in freelancing are welcome!💚✌️
